{"title" : "军营体验" ,"leftimage":["jyjx1.jpg","jyjx2.jpg","jyjx3.jpg"],"content":"<P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>军营体验是专为青少年打造的拓展项目之一。以全封闭式军事化训练特点而著称。日常生活均采用部队的军事化生活管理办法。纪律与服从是军营集训的第一要旨。</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><?xml:namespace prefix = 'o' ns = 'urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office' /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>军营体验融入了与青少年成长教育相匹配的拓展训练活动及内务训练活动。孩子们需要克服日常懒散的生活习惯、融入部队集体军事化的生活当中来，通过各项拓展活动的集体配合，培养孩子们的自立与团队荣誉感，同时军营生活可培养孩子们良好的日常生活</SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体'>习惯。</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp; </SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>报名参加办法：</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp;</SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>本项目学校团体、家庭、个人均可报名，非团体满</SPAN>6<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>组家庭或</SPAN>10<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>人成班，提前一周报名。 </SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='LAYOUT-GRID-MODE: char; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-layout-grid-align: none'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 5.9pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: .49'><B style='mso-bidi-font-weight: normal'><U style='text-underline: thick'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'></SPAN></U></B>&nbsp;</P>"}